Checker: enumSmallB (full small-clock phase enumeration 5*7*11*13 = 5005,
  NO mirror reduction) -> dfsB over the big clocks (min-uncovered-offset
  anchor, branching over remaining clocks x the two phases covering the
  anchor, exact residual-capacity prune).  Capacities are read off base-2^16
  residue-count words (resWord/digit) -- same exact values as the solver's
  histogram, so the traversal and node counts above stay the Lean-canonical
  reference (asserted per scale: 464 / 2,626 / 5,301 / 11,527 / 30,079 /
  25,543 dfs nodes).
